item.title: Super Bowl Boulevard Is In High Gear
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Take a photo with the Vince Lombardi Trophy! Receive FREE autographs from NFL players! Kick a field goal through NFL uprights! Visit the broadcast sets of NFL Network, ESPN and FOX! Ride the 60 foot toboggan ($5 per ride donated to MillionTreesNYC)! Visit NFL sponsor displays and receive FREE giveaways!
